query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(b1 q1 s t1 tq1 u1 acc) */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 5 AND q1.favorite_count <= 5000
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('browser',
'css-selectors',
'intellij-idea',
'jackson',
'methods',
'nlp',
'select')
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name = 'stackoverflow'
inner join badge AS b1
on s.site_id = b1.site_id AND b1.user_id = u1.id
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id AND acc.website_url ilike '%en';
